# MedSure Healthcare Services. 
MedSure Health Services is a midsize healthcare provider supporting clinical operations, patient services, and digital health platforms across multiple locations in Texas. The organization employs approximately 5,000 staff, with 20% working remotely, accessing critical systems such as electronic health records (EHR), patient portals, and cloud-based services. This organization also manages sensitive data which including;

1.  Protected Health Information (PHI)
2.  Personally Identifiable Information (PII)
3.  Financial data

Making cybersecurity and regulatory compliance a critical organizational priority. MedSure Health have other operational eenvironment that requires a risk based assessment these includes;

IT Environment:

On-prem EHR system

Cloud-based patient portal

Hybrid Active Directory

Medical devices (IoT)

Third-party billing vendor